snippet.title: ScourgeBringer Nintendo Switch Announcement - Europe
snippet.description:
ScourgeBringer is a fast-paced free-moving roguelite platformer. Help Kyhra to explore the unknown and slash her way through ancient machines guarding the seal of her past, and maybe the redemption of humanity. 
Now coming to Switch!

Join Flying Oak Discord to know more about the game’s development:
discord.gg/flyingoak
 
More news about the game on developers social media:
https://twitter.com/FlyingOakGames

Dear Villagers:
https://twitter.com/DearVillagers
https://www.facebook.com/DearVillagers/
